</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,151,825]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,464,583,608]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">Description of female</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation box="[485,563,583,607]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 2" captionStartId="1.[151,264,1960,1983]" captionTargetBox="[325,1265,196,1924]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[297,1286,193,1947]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 2. Matrona taoi sp. nov., damselflies photographed in the field in Xuan Son by Phan Quoc Toan on 15 December 2010. 1) male; 2) female." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/203454/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">
Figs 
<number box="[547,563,583,607]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" value="2.4">2</number>
</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[580,595,583,607]" captionStart="FIGURES 3 – 4" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1726,1749]" captionTargetBox="[234,1309,228,1672]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[187,1399,193,1705]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 3 – 4. Matrona taoi sp. nov. 3) habitus of paratype male (right hind wing incomplete at base)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/203455/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">4</figureCitation>
): Head and thorax coloured as in male. Wings (
<figureCitation box="[1179,1251,583,607]" captionStart="FIGURES 5 – 6" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1738,1761]" captionTargetBox="[309,1245,226,1681]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[309,1277,193,1717]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 5 – 6. Matrona taoi sp. nov. 5) wings of paratype male; 6) wings of paratype female." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/203456/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">
Fig. 
<number box="[1237,1251,583,607]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" value="6.0">6</number>
</figureCitation>
) reddish-brown throughout, an obscure darker band in the apical third of hind wing, the darker colour extending basad along wing border. Venation reddish brown to pale brown. Reticulation as sparse as in male. Median space of fore wing with 
<number box="[151,193,692,716]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" value="2.0" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="1.0">1–3</number>
crossveins; 
<number box="[338,380,692,716]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" value="3.0" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="2.0">2–4</number>
crossveins in hind wing. Cubital space with 
<number box="[907,976,692,716]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" value="20.5" valueMax="23.0" valueMin="18.0">18–23</number>
crossveins in fore wing, 
<quantity box="[1274,1377,692,716]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.207" metricValueMax="5.842" metricValueMin="4.572" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" unit="in" value="20.5" valueMax="23.0" valueMin="18.0">18–23 in</quantity>
hind wing. Quadrangle with 
<number box="[420,490,727,751]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" value="16.0" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="12.0">12–20</number>
crossveins in fore wing, 
<quantity box="[779,879,727,751]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.318" metricValueMax="4.826" metricValueMin="3.81" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" unit="in" value="17.0" valueMax="19.0" valueMin="15.0">15–19 in</quantity>
hind wing. Antenodals (in the first row) number 
<quantity box="[151,251,764,788]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2573" metricValueMax="1.3716" metricValueMin="1.143" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" unit="in" value="49.5" valueMax="54.0" valueMin="45.0">45–54 in</quantity>
fore wing and 
<quantity box="[426,526,764,788]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.1303" metricValueMax="1.2192" metricValueMin="1.0413999999999999" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" unit="in" value="44.5" valueMax="48.0" valueMin="41.0">41–48 in</quantity>
hind wing. Pseudopterostigma yellowish cream, short, covering 
<number box="[1265,1306,764,788]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" value="7.5" valueMax="9.0" valueMin="6.0">6–9</number>
underlying cells. Abdomen dark reddish brown, the apical segments obscurely pale laterally.
</paragraph>
<caption box="[151,942,1660,1683]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/203457/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" targetBox="[184,1398,898,1659]" targetPageId="4">
